headline: McKesson ideaShare Empowers Independent Pharmacies to Innovate and Thrive
summary: IRVING, Texas, July 15, 2025--Last week, McKesson hosted more than 2,500 attendees representing independent pharmacies at the 2025 McKesson ideaShare conference in Nashville.
